Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you and I were wounded,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rin saved our lives with\N{\i1}her Medical Ninjutsu!{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:02:50.77,00:02:54.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,リンは いつも 医療忍術で\N命を救ってくれたんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she hadn't been there,\N{\i1}we'd both be dead by now!{\i0\i0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:02:54.64,00:02:59.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アイツがいなけりゃ オレもお前も\Nとっくに死んでたんだぞ！
